# errorx enforcement

You are working inside **Aisphere Kernel**. Business code MUST use `github.com/aisphereio/kernel/errorx` for all errors.

## Forbidden patterns (will fail CI)

In `handler/`, `service/`, `repository/`, `worker/`, `controller/`, `internal/`, `cmd/` Go files (NOT in `*_test.go`):

```go
// ❌ FORBIDDEN — use errorx instead
return errors.New("...")
return fmt.Errorf("...")
return nil, err              // raw error passthrough
panic(err)

// ❌ FORBIDDEN — dynamic value in error code
errorx.NotFound(errorx.Code("SKILL_"+id+"_NOT_FOUND"), "...")
```

## Required patterns

```go
// ✅ Validation error
return errorx.BadRequest("AIHUB_SKILL_NAME_REQUIRED", "技能名称不能为空")

// ✅ Not found
return errorx.NotFound("AIHUB_SKILL_NOT_FOUND", "技能不存在",
    errorx.WithMetadata("skill_id", id),
)

// ✅ Permission denied
return errorx.Forbidden("AIHUB_SKILL_DELETE_DENIED", "没有删除权限")

// ✅ Wrap underlying error
return errorx.Wrap(err, "AIHUB_SKILL_CREATE_FAILED",
    errorx.WithMessage("创建技能失败"),
    errorx.WithRetryable(true),
    errorx.WithMetadata("skill_id", id),
)
```

## Constructor cheatsheet

| Scenario | Constructor | HTTP | gRPC |
|---|---|---:|---|
| Validation failed | `errorx.BadRequest` | 400 | InvalidArgument |
| Not authenticated | `errorx.Unauthorized` | 401 | Unauthenticated |
| No permission | `errorx.Forbidden` | 403 | PermissionDenied |
| Resource missing | `errorx.NotFound` | 404 | NotFound |
| Already exists | `errorx.Conflict` | 409 | AlreadyExists |
| Request timeout | `errorx.RequestTimeout` | 408 | DeadlineExceeded |
| Rate limited | `errorx.TooManyRequests` | 429 | ResourceExhausted |
| Client closed | `errorx.ClientClosed` | 499 | Canceled |
| Internal error | `errorx.Internal` | 500 | Internal |
| Upstream down | `errorx.Unavailable` | 503 | Unavailable |
| Upstream timeout | `errorx.Timeout` | 504 | DeadlineExceeded |

## Error code naming

Format: `{DOMAIN}_{RESOURCE}_{REASON}` — uppercase snake_case.

```
✅ AIHUB_SKILL_NOT_FOUND
✅ IAM_TOKEN_INVALID
✅ MODEL_UPSTREAM_TIMEOUT

❌ skillNotFound         (camelCase)
❌ SKILL_123_NOT_FOUND   (dynamic ID in code)
❌ ERROR / FAILED        (too vague)
```

Dynamic values MUST go into `errorx.WithMetadata(key, value)`, NEVER into the error code.

## Metadata safety

```go
// ✅ Internal metadata (logs/audit only, auto-redacted for sensitive keys)
errorx.WithMetadata("raw_error", err.Error())
errorx.WithMetadata("skill_id", id)

// ✅ Public metadata (safe for HTTP/gRPC responses)
errorx.WithPublicMetadata("resource", "skill")

// ❌ NEVER put tokens/passwords/cookies in PublicMetadata
errorx.WithPublicMetadata("token", userToken)  // LEAK!
```

